               <p>CHARLES PEAKE. I live at Kennington-common. I was going through <placeName id="t18310908-327-crimeloc1678">Hatton-garden</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-327-crimeloc1678" type="placeName" value="Hatton-garden"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-327-crimeloc1678" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-327-off1676 t18310908-327-crimeloc1678"></join> last Monday, and felt a motion at my pocket; I turned round instantly, and seized the prisoner, who had two others with him - he produced my handkerchief to me immediately; it was safe just before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-327-person2357">
                  PATRICK 
                  WALLACE
