            . I am a Policeman. I took the prisoner in charge.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Two boys picked the gentleman's pocket, and threw the handkerchief at me; he turned round and seized me as I was going to deliver it to him.</p>
